{"service_name": "Business Continuity Planning", "service_id": "7183427023235566", "company_name": "Evolve Secure Solutions Limited", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Evolve Secure Solutions Limited\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Business Continuity Planning\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Business Continuity services are built on a practical understanding of current best practice, as applied across the public and private sectors. Our specialist G-Cloud service offering develops and implements the ISO 22301 plans and procedures for the cloud environment, ensuring an effective and efficient approach across all key elements.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Policy objectives, priorities and responsibilities for continuity of services\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Business Impact Analysis identifying key processes and activities\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Defines acceptable period of outage and Recovery Time Objectives (RTOs)\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Risk assessment of internal/external risk to key processes and activities\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Business Continuity Strategy for continuity of key process and activities\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     BC Plan to enable the strategy\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     BC Plan validation to ensure that the plan works\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensuring staff are familiar with their roles and responsibilities\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Our team are experienced BC practitioners in the public sector\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Designed to satisfy the demands of public sector management\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Increased levels of resilience for information, systems and applications\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Accuracy of Recovery Time Objectives, and Recovery Point Objectives\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Availability of information, data, applications for processes and activities\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Compliance with applicable and required standards, such as ISO 22301\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Integration with existing policy and decision making processes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Agile approach tailored to our customer for highly focused advice\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Independent advice that is non-partial and in your best interest\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Contingency and continuity of service assured by Evolve team approach\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     VFM services tailored to customer business imperatives and timescales\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Quality of Service assured by ISO9001, ISO27001, ISO14001, CESG certifications\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3800 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Termination costs apply\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92536/7183427023235566-pricing-document-2015-10-01-1329.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class